verbose_text: In this study, we found that celecoxib significantly increased caspase-8 and -9 mRNA expression in a time- and dose dependent manner in SGC-7901 cells, suggesting that celecoxib may activate caspase-8 and -9 to initiated apoptosis through the death receptor and mitochondrial pathways, respectively.
